---
title: Loaded Sweet Potato Mash with Greek style cheese, walnuts and mixed veg
description: This vibrant veggie recipe is loosely based on a traditional Dutch stamppot. Though there isn't a perfect equivalent in English, the word stamppot roughly translates to hotchpotch—a fitting name for this busy yet delicious dish.
